(1033, 1, '2012-07-30 15:52:32', '2012-07-30 12:52:32', '<p><span style="color: #043d65;"><strong>Three stamps for compliance...<br /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>ARCC &ndash; Pipe Spool Fabrication Plant (PSFP) obtained the ASME Certificate of Authorization for the three (3) Stamps (i.e. Boiler Assembly &lsquo;A&rsquo; Pressure Piping &lsquo;PP&rsquo;, Power Boiler &lsquo;S&rsquo;) and NB Stamp (Repair / Alteration &lsquo;R&rsquo;) to construct and verify components according to ASME Code Section I, B31.1 and NB-28. US-based ASME Auditor Team together with the Authorized Inspection Agency (Supervisor and Authorized Inspector) performed the audit of the company and ascertained the company&rsquo;s compliance to the requirements stipulated in ASME Code Section I, B31.1 and NB-28. the final audit was conducted in ARCC-PSFP located in Jubail.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Boiler Welding', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '80-revision-25', '', '', '2012-07-30 15:52:32', '2012-07-30 12:52:32', '', 80, '/arcc/?p=1033', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
