(596, 1, '2011-04-12 14:39:49', '2011-04-12 14:39:49', '<p>Taking pride in its Qurayyah Team Unity, the ARCC Team, continued to perform well in its shuddown works (boiler modification, oil burner replacement, and superheater extension work) as the project achieved another major milestone - initial firing of Boiler Unit No. 3 - on 29 January 2011 which is nine days ahead of schedule.</p>\r\n<p>Mitsubishi Corporation (MC) had issued to ARCC the Provision Acceptance Certificates for boiler Units No. 1 &amp; 2 completed earlier under Phase 1 wherein ARCC was commended by the senior level management of the Client, Saudi Electricity Comp. (SEC), for the good performance and quality of work.</p>\r\n<p><img alt="" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-94" height="288" src="/arcc-eei/wp-content/uploads/7-qurayyahupdate.jpg" title="7 - qurayyahupdate" width="750" /></p>\r\n', 'Qurayyah Team ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '275-revision-13', '', '', '2011-04-12 14:39:49', '2011-04-12 14:39:49', '', 275, 'http://www.alrushaidconstruction.com/arcc/?p=596', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
