(1011, 1, '2011-05-27 19:35:20', '2011-05-27 19:35:20', '<p>Taking pride in its Qurayyah Team Unity, the ARCC Team, continued to perform well in its shuddown works (boiler modification, oil burner replacement, and superheater extension work) as the project achieved another major milestone - initial firing of Boiler Unit No. 3 - on 29 January 2011 which is nine days ahead of schedule.</p>\r\n<p><img alt="" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-94" height="288" src="/arcc-eei/wp-content/uploads/7-qurayyahupdate.jpg" title="7 - qurayyahupdate" width="750" /></p>\r\n\r\n', 'Qurayyah Team Unity', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '273-revision-17', '', '', '2011-05-27 19:35:20', '2011-05-27 19:35:20', '', 273, '/arcc/?p=1011', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
