(1326, 1, '2012-08-04 06:58:35', '2012-08-04 03:58:35', '<p>ARCC &ndash; Pipe Spool Fabrication Plant (PSFP) obtained the ASME Certificate of Authorization for the three (3) Stamps (i.e. Boiler Assembly &lsquo;A&rsquo; Pressure Piping &lsquo;PP&rsquo;, Power Boiler &lsquo;S&rsquo;) and NB Stamp (Repair / Alteration &lsquo;R&rsquo;) to construct and verify components according to ASME Code Section I, B31.1 and NB-28. US-based ASME Auditor Team together with the Authorized Inspection Agency (Supervisor and Authorized Inspector) performed the audit of the company and ascertained the company&rsquo;s compliance to the requirements stipulated in ASME Code Section I, B31.1 and NB-28. the final audit was conducted in ARCC-PSFP located in Jubail.</p>', 'Boiler Welding', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '80-revision-27', '', '', '2012-08-04 06:58:35', '2012-08-04 03:58:35', '', 80, 'http://192.168.8.59/arcc/arcc/?p=1326', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
